Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a psychiatrist for 35 years, psychoanalyst, researcher into the\Nnature of nutrition and brain chemistry. I've been doing work for the last eight years on the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,nature of consciousness itself and its relationship to what the world calls spiritual. In this series\Nof talks, we're exploring the utilization of the knowledge that arises out of studying the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,nature of consciousness itself and its application to man's problems and especially his areas of\Nsuffering. So today's talk has to do with the nature of illness itself, the letting go of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:01:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,illness. And in it, I'll also bring in my own personal experiences as well as my clinical\Nobservations. We won't be talking about philosophy. We won't be talking about theory. We'll be talking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about what you and I can clinically verify in our own personal experience.\NThat which is true because we can verify it, which is really the basis of all of science. The ability
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to repeat, to reduplicate, to verify an observation and within your own personal experience and apply\Nit to your own individual problems and see if it works. So essentially, we're coming from sort of a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,radical pragmatism. We're going to believe that which we can prove to be true through our own\Nexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm in doing this we're going to be talking about the relationship between body, mind, and spirit. Is that just a catchphrase?\NIs that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mmm\Na wishful-thinking motto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it something real?\NWhat is the nature of spirit anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a metaphysical abstraction,\Na philosophic position,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,um, religious shibboleth? What is the exact nature\Nof body, mind & spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to bring about self-healing, because that's what we're talking about today, self-healing,\Nit's essential that we understand the relationship between the body and the mind and the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, we're going to say something we've said in our other talks,\Nand it has to be repeated over and over again before we finally get the truth of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body has no capacity to experience itself.\NThe arm cannot experience its armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The leg cannot experience its legness.\NThe body has no way in which to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The body itself is in sentient.\NInstead, what we experience are the sensations, sensations of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's the sensations of where the body is in space that we're experiencing.\NSensations themselves, curiously enough, have no capacity to experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensations have to be experienced in something that is greater than that, and that is mind itself.\NIt's within mind that the experience of the sensations and what they report about the body is experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ablate part of mind, then that opposite side of the body, let's say, is no longer experienced.\NIt's necessary for mind then to be there to experience the sensations which then report the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprising as it may sound also, mind cannot experience itself.\NA thought cannot experience its thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling cannot experience its own feelingness.\NMemory cannot experience its own memoryness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be experienced in something greater than that.\NYou see, our principle is that each thing is experienced from an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which is less restricted, which is less limited.\NIt is always experienced in something that is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that mind itself then is experienced because of the energy field of consciousness itself.\NConsciousness, that which is formless, that which is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie screen upon which we experience the moving of the movie.\NIt is because of consciousness then that we experience what is in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole basis of anesthesia, remove consciousness and there's no experience of either mind or body.\NConsciousness itself is experienced in something greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the infinite energy field called awareness itself.\NIt is because of awareness that we know what is going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of consciousness that we know what is going on in mind.\NIt is because of mind that we know what the senses are reporting about the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we can see that that which we are,\Nthat which we are really is several levels removed from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it rather clear that we are not the body, we are that which is aware,\Nthat which is conscious and within that consciousness, the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,These are very important things to realize and you can sit down in a very short meditation,\Nverify the truth of this for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That you are that.\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is aware of all these lesser levels of reality.\NWe'll go back to what we're going to be talking about today specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual techniques of self-healing, how they're brought about, how they're applied,\Nwhat the basic principles are and we'll be looking at topics such as
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of all illness is unconscious guilt plus a specific belief system\Naggravated by suppressed emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll describe how I myself utilizing these techniques and these understandings\Nand these basic principles I healed myself of about 20 chronic intractable illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which had been totally refractory to traditional medical treatment\Nincluding how I let go of wearing glasses after 40 years of wearing glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go through it step by step.\NWe'll see how illness is also a result of buying into the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and how not to buy into it.\NHow illness comes about as a result of family belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look at the fact that all illnesses are recoverable.\NThere is no order of difficulty no matter how severe they may sound to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How to energize that self-healer which is present in everyone.\NAnd we'll look at a curious thing which demonstrates the truths of many of the things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be saying today and that is the phenomena of multiple personality.\NThose people who some of whom become patients of course
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and which science and psychiatry is looking at with increasing interest\Nbecause they explain so many different phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where more than one personality expresses itself through the body usually alternately.\NAnd we'll look at the curious clinical fact that one personality may have multiple illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,may have ulcers let's say and asthma\Nand allergies and gout and a whole variety of illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that personality leaves and the other personality comes in.\NThat other personality may well have none of those illnesses whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That personality may say I don't believe in any of those things.\NI'm not subject to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:08:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we'll be looking at the power of mind.\NThe power of mind over body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be looking at a basic principle of self-healing that I am only subject to what I hold in mind.\NAnd to make this understandable then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we can make sense rather than sounding mystical or puzzling in our expressions.\NWe'll be referring as we have in all of these talks to this chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To this map of consciousness.\NA mathematical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A useful construct.\NIn which we have the various energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have them calibrated as to their relative power.\NAnd we have the energy fields calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as to the direction of the field.\NWhether it is a negative energy field with a destructive influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a positive energy field.\NIt'll be necessary to know a few of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to feel confident that we're operating out of something that is reasonable and understandable.\NRather than just taking my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sharing my personal experience because that personal experience\Nis merely the demonstration of the basic truths we'll be talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Merely a demonstration of things that you know unconsciously.\NBut today we're going to merely make it conscious so that you can use it as a therapeutic tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How to not buy into programs.\NAnd we'll be looking at what it means to be programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To buy into a thought system because the mind is so powerful.\NThat what it believes tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have in fact a very interesting study that we'll refer to in a recent issue of Brain Mind Journal.\NBrain Mind Bulletin. January 1987.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As a prelude to what we'll be talking about later.\NHere's a very interesting study. The title is Expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What you see is what they give you.\NIt says at Princeton University research has shown
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the self-fulfilling prophecy is just that.\NIt says what we actively believe tends to manifest in our behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the behavior of others.\NThis is what they call a created social reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A serious issue that affects everything from stock prices to the arms race.\NNot to mention everyday interactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I might add all the details of one's personal health.\NThe basic premise from which we'll be operating is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that all phenomena are experienced in consciousness.\NIf all phenomena are experienced in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is in consciousness that the experience of man is going on.\NThen we will address ourself to the level of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And its expression in mind.\NWe'll go to the level of cause instead of the level of effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The body then is the effect of what is held in mind.\NIf we want to know what we're holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is look at what is going on in the body.\NAnd its behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that'll tell us what we believe.\NIf we look back into our memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We often will not be able to recall that we had any such belief system.\NOr that we thought that it applied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the very fact that it is in our life tells us it must have been there somewhere in the unconscious.\NThe most common example I see of this is in people who are allergic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And people will say well I didn't have any belief in allergies.\NI didn't bring this into my life consciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet if we go back into their childhood almost invariably.\NWe will find that the belief system in allergies occurred very early in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often ages two or three.\NThe little child picks up a remark by someone in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as allergies run in our family.\NThe minute the child's mind buys this, hears it, of course believes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This now becomes an operative program.\NAnd so a lot of the phenomena that we're going to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressing itself in the body.\NIn the adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was picked up very early in life by a chance remark.\NSomething heard on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Something misunderstood in a book.\NA remark that a teacher made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And these things will become conscious as we begin to work on them.\NWe're only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what must we be holding in mind?\NWhat is the nature of illness itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the nature of illness is first of all pain and suffering.\NConsequently it's clear and obvious and merely common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That illness is an expression of pain and suffering.\NAnd if we look at our chart over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is pain and suffering?\NPain and suffering is down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At the lowest energy level.\NAnd we'll see that the energy field of that is in a negative direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning that it has a negative effect on our life.\NSo we have to look into the nature of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of unconscious guilt.\NAnd how it expresses itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll see that the thought patterns in the mind.\NOur belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which unconscious guilt has grabbed onto.\NTo express this energy field of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And where does the guilt come from?\NThe guilt comes from judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,From all the negative opinions and judgments.\NAll these negative energy fields collectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that all these negative feelings tend to go together.\NEverything below the level of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the energy field suddenly swings to the positive.\NAll have arrows going in this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these negative feelings then contribute to illness.\NPride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger.\NDesire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear.\NGrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy.\NGuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We know with kinesiology where you test a person's muscle strength.\NThat if they hold in mind anything below the energy of courage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hold a prideful thought.\NAn angry thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A wantingness.\NA cravingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A fearful thought.\NSome grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy.\NGuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A guilty thought.\NAny of these kinds of expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These feelings over here.\NRegret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uselessness.\NDespair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-hatred.\NWorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety.\NGrievances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Any kind of arrogance or contempt.\NWe know that with kinesiology the person instantly goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does that represent?\NThat represents a desynchronization of the cerebral hemispheres.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An instant weakening of the body's energy field.\NIt represents something that is deleterious to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we know.\NAnd it can be tested and proven to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That any negative thought or feeling itself desynchronizes the body's acupuncture energy system.\NThat energy system which is even more rapid than the central nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And far more rapid than the autonomic sympathetic nervous system.\NThat the body's acupuncture energy system which are the energies flowing down the acupuncture meridians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12 main meridians of the body.\NInstantly responds to anything that is negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that is not the truth.\NBecause all these energy fields below the level of courage here represent that which is not the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is not the truth then brings in the whole energy field of being victim.\NAnd as a sick person we view ourselves as a victim of the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's important then to realize that there is the illness.\NAnd then there is the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who has the illness.\NHow to be with that illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we realize that the person who is with that illness has to change in order for the illness to disappear.\NToday we'll be talking about the specifics of healing a specific illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How to handle the actual event on the physical, psychological, emotional, mental level.\NAnd how one must become as a being so that healing becomes automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We see from this chart that all the negative emotions create illness.\NAnd that all the positive emotions heal illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:17:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that once we get above the level of courage.\NA level that we cross by telling the truth about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We become detached.\NThat opens a space for us to become willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To be an accepting person.\NTo become a loving person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And love as an energy field on this calibrated scale where death is zero.\NLove comes out at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And healing comes out about 540.\NWhat kind of lovingness then brings about an almost automatic healing within the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that it's unconditional love.\NUnconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is non-judgmental.\NThat which is forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is aligned with understanding and compassion.\NThat which nurtures and supports all of life and honors its sacredness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:18:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That which sees the sacredness of life, supports and honors it, of itself creates a healing energy field.\NAn energy field which we calibrate on our mathematical model at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How to become that.\NThe kind of a person in whom healing begins to occur automatically because of the level and the general nature of our consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, how to bring about a healing of a specific illness.\NIn healing the specifics of an illness, which we'll address first, because we'll be talking about sort of the mechanics of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be utilizing some techniques that we've talked about in other talks in this series.\NWe have to begin by letting go, resisting the sensations that we're experiencing and stop labeling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said, you cannot experience a duodenal ulcer.\NYou cannot experience asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all mental constructs.\NThose are all elaborate programs and belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot experience asthma.\NWhat do you experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is where our technique of radical truth comes up.\NWe go into the inner experience of the exact sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We let go, resisting them.\NWe, in effect, will eventually disappear them by aligning ourselves with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by welcoming these inner experiences of the sensations.\NAnd at the same time, within mind, we cancel any labels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We stop calling it ulcer.\NAnd instead, we go into what is the inner sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner sensation is of a pressure, or a burning, let us say.\NBurning and pressure, I want you to get, are also labels and names.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We cancel those, and we again go into what is the core,\Nthe absolute essential of what it is we're experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we let go, resisting that experience.\NSo the actual healing of the physicality of the illness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is letting go, resisting,\Nthe inner experience of it, without any mental label.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, in fact, we begin to cancel that mental label,\Nand we cancel it, and replace it with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel. We say, I no longer believe in that.\NI am an infinite being, and I am not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean, I'm an infinite being, and I'm not subject to that?\NIt means I'm only limited to my belief systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I let my belief systems go, what takes its place?\NIf I remove form from consciousness, what is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is left is the formless.\NFormless, by its definition, by the inner experience of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite, without boundaries, without beginning, without end.\NThat which is the essential nature of consciousness itself is unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we place a limitation, if we interject form,\Nthen what happens is we subject ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to what we are holding in mind.\NAnd so, to replace it, what we do is we consciously cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, I cancel any belief in duodenal ulcers, asthma,\Nwhatever the illness might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say, I am only subject to what I hold in mind.\NI'm an infinite being, and in truth, I am not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is a fact.\NIf we test that with kinesiology, we will see that is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we test a person and we say, cancel, I am not subject to that,\NI am an infinite being, I am only subject to what I hold in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we will see they instantly go strong,\Nindicating that this is a statement of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, we replace that which is false by that which is true.\NWe replace the lie by the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what is the effect then on our energy, fuels, and consciousness?\NThe lie, by its nature, puts us below the line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and throws us into a negative energy field,\Nwhich in and of itself brings about illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute we tell the truth, the energy field,\Nas you see here at the level of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,courage meaning the courage to tell the truth,\Nthat you are an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are only subject to what you hold in mind,\Ninstantly puts you above the line. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to accept this truth puts you up here.\NThe acceptance of this truth puts you up as far as here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we are now in a position to choose\Nthat position called lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness.\NThe lovingness of the body instead of the make wrong of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The lovingness of our life instead of the make wrong of our life.\NThe lovingness of the being that we are instead of the criticism of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we find that we have to let go of criticism.\NWe have to let go of attack thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,critical thoughts, judgmental thoughts.\NWe have to let go of putting ourselves in the position
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of being right and other people wrong.\NWhy is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the level of right and wrong is about an energy field of 180\Nand we see that 180 is a negative thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it has a deleterious effect on our health,\Non our life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let that go.\NSo if I am willing to let go of my illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have to be willing to let go of the attitudes\Nthat brought that illness about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because disease is an expression then of attitudes,\Nof habitual ways of looking at things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the specifics of healing a particular illness then\Nis letting go resisting the experience of it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop labeling it, stop putting names on it.\NAnd to use no words at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go experiencing what you are experiencing\Nin a very radical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time to cancel the thought form,\Nto cancel the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this so?\NWe said that the energy field of love itself heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.59,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To put yourself in an energy field of 540\Nis automatically to heal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A loving thought then heals\Nand a negative thought creates illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To choose to become a loving person then.\NTo choose to become a loving person
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,actually within the brain begins to release endorphins.\NAnd these endorphins have a profound effect
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,on the body's health and happiness.\NWe know that health and happiness go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness then arises from this\Nand the willingness to let go of that which is negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.19,0:24:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what replaces it in consciousness\Nis love itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.19,0:24:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the essential nature of consciousness\Nunless it's been impaired
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.19,0:24:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is a lovingness.\NWe see this in the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.19,0:24:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We see it in the young child whose innocence and lovingness\Nis the expression of the essence of human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it hasn't been programmed yet\Nto go into fear, to go into doubt, to go into limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.25,0:25:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that essential expression of lovingness\Nwhich we need to recapture
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.25,0:25:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal any illness within ourself is critical.\NThe letting go of the negativity of the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we pick up these belief systems?\NWe have to cancel specific belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We pick it up through television.\NWe pick it up through well-intentioned people who want to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.70,0:25:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and their intention is to prevent these illnesses in us\Nby educating us about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.70,0:25:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead what we find is that the mind now is programmed\Nto believe in a specific belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then unconscious guilt comes up\Nand utilizes this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.80,0:25:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And through the acupuncture energy system\Nand its interference with the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,running down through the 12 meridians\Nwe find an impairment of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.30,0:26:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,flowing into a specific body system.\NSo let us say every time I go below the line
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.80,0:26:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we're calling this level here of courage the line.\NAny time we go below the line
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.80,0:26:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,if we test somebody we find that their energy system just blows out.\NIf the energy system blows out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.80,0:26:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,characteristically most people will blow one meridian\Nrather than another.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.80,0:26:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So let us say a person habitually every time\Nthey have one of these negative thoughts or feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.30,0:26:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of their negative belief systems\Nevery time they have a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.80,0:26:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they blow the heart meridian.\NAs the years go by every time they have a resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,every time they go into self-pity\Nany time they criticize someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.80,0:26:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,every second that they do that\Nit blows the energy flow down the heart meridian.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.80,0:26:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that meridian is flowing the life energy\Nthe energy of life itself into the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.80,0:26:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the impairment of the flow\Nof the energy of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.46,0:27:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To the heart in subtle very delicate ways\Nbegins to alter the physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to express itself through irregularities\Nin the autonomic nervous system
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.96,0:27:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that nervous system which operates\Nin the functioning of body organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.52,0:27:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we begin to have an impairment\Nof the physiology of the heart itself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.52,0:27:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lining of the arteries.\NAnd so as the years go by
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.52,0:27:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the habitual blowing of the heart meridian then\Nbrings an impairment on the physical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.02,0:27:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we now see\Nthe expression on the physical level
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which was held in mind.\NThat is our basic premise, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.52,0:27:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That the body expresses what is held in mind\Nnot vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is now expressing\Nthe person's habit of thinking in a negative way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.53,0:27:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mechanics of that are to blow the acupuncture system\Nblow the autonomic system
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.53,0:28:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,blow the sensitive\Nelectrical and chemical things
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which are going on in the cells\Nand you begin to get
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.53,0:28:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the development of pathologic changes\Nwithin the anatomy and dysfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And this dysfunction then results let's say\Nin a coronary or heart disease
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.53,0:28:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or heart failure.\NSo the heart failure then came about
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.53,0:28:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of the mental attitudes.\NThe mind would like to blame it on cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.63,0:28:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or blame it on stress.\NBlame it on one style of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.63,0:28:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Blame it on genetics.\NBlame it on what goes on in our family, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.61,0:28:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that those are all merely explanations.\NThose are only excuses and rationalizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.61,0:28:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to make intelligible\Nthat which is not clearly defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.61,0:28:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at the exact mechanics we see that\Nexactly what we said in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.11,0:29:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is exactly what's happening.\NWhat we hold in mind begins to manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on the physical plane.\NYou see it is mind that has the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mind that has the power.\NWhen you think of it one thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.61,0:29:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say you have a thought\NI think I'll go to Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That one thought now energizes your finances.\NIt determines what you're going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.11,0:29:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,over the next six months getting ready for this trip.\NYou see the thought held in mind now determines
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.61,0:29:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do with your money, your whole behavior,\Nthe packing, the getting ready for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.61,0:29:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves your body thousands of miles through the air.\NThe one thought energized the next six months of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.11,0:29:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how powerful mind is.\NAnd one of the difficulties to be overcome in self-healing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is the acceptance, the willingness to accept\Nthe great power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.17,0:29:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot let a negative thought go unchallenged.\NYou cannot say I have diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and let that go unchallenged.\NThat is a belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.67,0:30:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That belief system is so powerful\Nthat the belief system I have diabetes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.67,0:30:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,alone is sufficient to create diabetes.\NInstead you have to cancel it and say
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.67,0:30:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a person who once thought that.\NBut I am only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.17,0:30:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an infinite being and I'm not subject to that.\NAnd instead you release on any symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.67,0:30:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You cancel them.\NYou replace them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.68,0:30:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with the truth.\NAnd in doing that you move above the line
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.18,0:30:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the specifics of a given illness.\NAnd when I get to an account of how I use this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.18,0:30:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in getting rid of 15 or 20 illnesses within myself,\Nperhaps these principles will become more apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.18,0:30:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I myself had such a list of illnesses\Nthat frankly I have to write them all down
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.16,0:30:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to remember them\Nbecause half of them have been forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.16,0:30:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet all of them lasted for many, many years.\NI had a duodenal ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.29,0:30:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was intractable.\NI was on all the traditional medical treatments
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.29,0:30:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and had psychoanalysis and a whole variety of things\Nthat began in medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.61,0:31:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And 20 years later I still had the ulcer.\NAnd not only that but it was a different ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.61,0:31:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was making holes in other parts of my duodenum\Nand it was threatening to perforate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.61,0:31:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was threatening to hemorrhage.\NAnd it was bringing about recurrent attacks of diverticulitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.61,0:31:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm sorry, pancreatitis.\NAt the same time I also had colitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.16,0:31:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time I also had diverticulitis.\NIn fact, I had diverticulitis so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.16,0:31:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that I landed in the hospital with it several times\Nand had to have transfusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.16,0:31:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I almost hemorrhaged to death with it.\NI also had migraine headaches which were intractable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And psychoanalysis had helped it to some degree.\NAnd I had seen neurologists and very famous world experts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.75,0:31:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was really no help for the migraine\Nand the migraine was associated with many allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.75,0:31:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sensitive to inhalants, things in the atmosphere.\NI couldn't walk into a place that had been exterminated
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.75,0:32:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,within the last couple of weeks.\NI could detect one part in a million
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would react with a migraine headache.\NThe prostate was enlarged
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.04,0:32:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had all those problems that go on physically\Nin the general GU tract of middle-aged men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.17,0:32:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Raynaud's disease, a vibration disease\Nthat was impairing the blood flow into the extremities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.17,0:32:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had threatening gangrene of the fingertips\Nand circulatory impairment of the hands and feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was cold all the time.\NOn top of that I had gout and a high uric acid level.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.87,0:32:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course I was on a diet for that.\NAnd I had gouty arthritis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.87,0:32:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I carried a cane in the back of my car.\NImagine carrying a cane in the back of your car
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.06,0:32:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because when gout comes on it comes out very suddenly.\NAnd it's very, very paralyzing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.56,0:32:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I carried a cane in the back of the car for many years.\NAt the same time I had severe hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.72,0:33:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't eat sugar or sweets or starches or anything like that.\NSo on top of all the allergies and the ulcer and the diverticulitis
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other gastrointestinal problems I had\Nand the pancreatitis and the occasional gallbladder attack, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.85,0:33:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there were frankly very few things I could eat.\NI would go to a restaurant sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.85,0:33:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only thing I could eat was the lettuce and the salad.\NI couldn't eat the tomatoes, of course, because of the seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.85,0:33:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It might aggravate the diverticulitis.\NAnd I was also 50 pounds overweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.49,0:33:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I described, of course, how I handled the weight problem\Nin the talk that I gave on weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.72,0:33:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we had things wrong with the gastrointestinal tract\Nfrom one end to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.72,0:33:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Things wrong with the circulatory system from one end to the other.\NThings wrong with the digestive system, the circulatory system,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.22,0:33:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the hormonal balance, the blood chemistries.\NI had elevated blood cholesterol, elevated blood uric acid,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:34:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,impairments in the self-regulatory mechanisms,\Nmigraine headaches and things indicating stress and pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.00,0:34:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,within the central nervous system\Nand its impairment of the autonomic nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.00,0:34:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's enough to start with.\NOn top of that I had a cystic tumor which would require surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.50,0:34:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a thing that spontaneously disappears.\NAnd so that's about where I was at age 50
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.00,0:34:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when I really got serious about researching the nature of consciousness\Nand its application to spiritual principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.00,0:34:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Systems now had to be questioned and looked at.\NWhat was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.00,0:34:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's obvious that a person who has that many illnesses\Ncan hardly be said to love themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.19,0:34:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I began with perfectionism.\NI began to see how this perfectionistic tendency,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.20,0:34:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,which allowed me to forgive others but did not allow me to forgive myself,\Nwas creating an intolerance of my own humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.20,0:35:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, as you see, to be intolerant, to condemn,\Nto attack all these things within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.46,0:35:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of this kind of guilt.\NThe feeling of guilt about one's own humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.46,0:35:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I had to move to a willingness to accept\Nand to love, to love and to forgive my own humanness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.05,0:35:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,all this basket of negativity,\Nthat it was only human to have these kind of feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.55,0:35:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go attacking myself for being human.\NAnd so I had to look into the essence then
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.05,0:35:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of seeing what is the essential, what is the inner core,\Nthe essence of one's humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.05,0:35:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this brought me to the awareness\Nof the intrinsic innocence within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:36:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to look then at the nature of consciousness.\NHow does the child, in its innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in its lack of negativity,\Nend up with so many programs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.20,0:36:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,within mind as to create all these illnesses?\NAnd we look at the nature then of innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.08,0:36:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can see it if we track what happens to it in the child.\NYou see, the child's innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.90,0:36:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the child might even be compared to the hardware of a computer.\NThe hardware of a computer is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.03,0:36:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the software that goes through the hardware\Nthat creates the output.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.62,0:36:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardware of the computer, however,\Nis not affected by the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.12,0:36:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the child and we see the innocence of its consciousness.\NHow does all the negative programming come into the innocent child?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.10,0:37:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes in because of its innocence.\NIt's because the child is innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.10,0:37:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that it believes anything it is told.\NIt's out of its lovingness and its trust
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.42,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of its parents and its teacher\Nand of the world and of television
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and of commercials and of society\Nthen that it becomes programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.42,0:37:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the innocence of the child is no longer so observable\Nbecause now what we're observing are all the programs
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.42,0:37:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that the innocent child has picked up.\NOut of its innocence, it believes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the prejudices of its parents and its playmates.\NThe little sly remarks that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.42,0:37:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't play with certain kinds of people, etc.\NWhat bought that program?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.42,0:37:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What bought that negative program?\NThe innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.42,0:37:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that innocence remains\Nwithin our consciousness throughout our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.99,0:37:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always going on.\NIt's out of the innocence that we buy error.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.99,0:38:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But the innocence itself is unsullied.\NAnd we have to go back into the recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.12,0:38:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of that inner innocence\Nin order to forgive ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.12,0:38:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and to forgive others.\NIt's that inner innocence that allows us to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.26,0:38:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,learn anything new, you see.\NThat innocence of the child never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.92,0:38:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it is the innocence of the child within you\Nthat is listening to my voice this very second.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.90,0:38:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It has never changed.\NIt is that same trusting, believing,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.40,0:38:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hoping to hear the truth,\Nopen to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.03,0:38:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that same trusting innocence that goes on.\NEven if you don't believe what you're hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or you don't believe\Nwhat you're hearing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.44,0:38:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're doing it because of some\Nopposite program within your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.44,0:38:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that says, let's say,\Ndon't trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.94,0:38:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And what bought that program,\Ndon't trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.94,0:39:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your innocence.\NIt's because you're innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.94,0:39:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you bought that program.\NDon't trust anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So even the untrusting person\Nis doing it out of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.44,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trusting the truth of that statement,\Nisn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.94,0:39:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe one day,\Nyou know, his father says,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.94,0:39:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,don't trust anybody out there, you see.\NAnd it was innocence that bought the distrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.01,0:39:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So innocence itself is unsullied, untouched.\NIt never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.01,0:39:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the nature of consciousness itself.\NIt's the hardware of the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.01,0:39:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many negative software programs\Nand floppy disks you play through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.01,0:39:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the hardware is untouched, unsullied.\NIt remains the same, pristine and pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.01,0:39:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That inner pristine purity then\Nis still within all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.80,0:39:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that brings us then to compassion.\NCompassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.58,0:39:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We see then\Nhow we picked up programs as we grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.06,0:40:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of pride, let's say, in adolescence.\NOr the young boy that I was, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.67,0:40:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of pride.\NYou don't want to admit that you have fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have desire,\Nthat you have feelings of loss
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.67,0:40:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and regret and hopelessness.\NThese are not manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.67,0:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The self-hatred that then accumulates,\Nthe guilt that accumulates,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.17,0:40:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the constant rejection of your own humanness.\NAnd so we have to move to a way of being with ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a healing way of being with ourself.\NAnd what I'm talking about is easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.83,0:40:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's merely choosing to be compassionate.\NChoosing to be forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.83,0:40:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the decision comes\Nto be that way about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.83,0:40:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To be that way about others.\NBecause if I am that way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.33,0:40:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,about others,\Nthen automatically I am that way about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am that way about myself,\NI automatically become that way about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.36,0:41:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that which I forgive in others,\NI automatically am forgiving in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.44,0:41:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all I'm seeing out there\Nis myself projected into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I forgive it in myself,\Nthen I also forgive it in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.60,0:41:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what happens then\Nis the beginning of the undoing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.60,0:41:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of all this negativity.\NThe replacement of all these negative low energies
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.10,0:41:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by a positive plus 500 or 540 energy.\NAs we do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.23,0:41:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to experience the world and ourself differently.\NOur relationship to life differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.23,0:41:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin to experience an inner joy.\NAn inner joyfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.23,0:41:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When we begin to see the results\Nof our willingness to let go our condemnations
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.23,0:41:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of ourself and others.\NWhat happens is we begin to make this a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.69,0:41:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way we are in the world.\NIt's a decision that we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.19,0:41:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That that's the kind of a person\Nthat we are choosing to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.69,0:42:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A powerful decision.\NA powerful intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.22,0:42:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That intention to be\Na source of healing to yourself and to others
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.22,0:42:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,then sets up a context.\NContext.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.22,0:42:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What does context mean?\NIntention sets up context.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.14,0:42:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our intention to be this kind of a person then,\Nsets up the whole energy of our consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.92,0:42:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and aligns it so that we begin to see things that way.\NIn other words, there is an actual alteration of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We literally begin to see the world\Nthrough forgiving eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.92,0:42:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Through healing eyes.\NThrough compassionate eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.92,0:42:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sympathy.\NWe're not talking about sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is down in the lower energy fields.\NWe're talking about a lovingness as an inner decision
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.42,0:42:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to be that kind of a human being\Ntowards our self and towards others.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.92,0:43:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness, the willingness\Nto let go of our criticalness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.42,0:43:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,our moralistic right and wrong,\Npolarizing our self with others by saying
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.42,0:43:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my position is right and your position is wrong.\NBecause the body expresses what the mind believes,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.29,0:43:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind, this decision then,\Nbegins to affect the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.29,0:43:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And we track down the mechanics of that with kinesiology.\NWe said that when you hold a loving thought in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.29,0:43:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if you picture somebody,\Nyou can have anybody in your family test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.67,0:43:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold out your arm and you resist\Nand you hold a loving thought in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.67,0:43:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do that, you'll see you're strong.\NNow you hold an unloving thought in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.67,0:43:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see you instantly go weak.\NThe body is instantly reflecting what the mind believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.67,0:43:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move into this decision then\Nto be forgiving and compassionate,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.28,0:43:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to be that which supports life\Nand nurtures it instead of condemns it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.78,0:43:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or moralistically puts it down\Nand gets into a make wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.28,0:44:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,our willingness to let go of make wrongs.\NWe let go attacking ourself for being ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.82,0:44:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people who get into spiritual work\Nor metaphysical studies, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,will compound it by making themself wrong\Nbecause they have a physical illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.82,0:44:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness to accept whatever is being expressed\Non the physical level
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.92,0:44:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and our willingness to look within our own consciousness\Nto see what is bringing about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.92,0:44:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is what is being brought to our attention.\NSo that everything that's happening in our life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.92,0:44:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening in order to come up to be healed.\NSo instead of being ashamed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.92,0:44:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're a spiritual seeker, let's say,\Nand that we have a physical illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.92,0:44:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,instead we become thankful\Nsee, gratitude, and we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.92,0:44:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,aha, something is coming up\Nin order to be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.92,0:44:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, once you have that capacity,\Nonce you've activated that which is healing within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.42,0:45:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is it brings up the various things to be healed.\NSo it's a sign of progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.92,0:45:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,not a sign of falling back at all.\NWe can be happy that we have a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.62,0:45:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal these things.\NSo an illness then is merely
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.62,0:45:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,our consciousness\Ncalling attention to something that needs to be looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.12,0:45:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in which we're feeling guilty.\NThere's some belief system we're holding
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.12,0:45:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to be let go of and cancelled.\NThere's something that has to be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.12,0:45:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something within us that has to be loved.\NSo we thank it then for bringing it to our awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.01,0:45:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, thank you, ulcer.\NI see you forced me to look at the way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.51,0:45:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I was condemning myself\Nand not loving myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.01,0:45:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, hypoglycemia,\Nfor showing me how much I've been living in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.01,0:45:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You thank all your illnesses then\Nbecause they have brought you to that willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.01,0:45:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to that acceptance,\Nto move into that field of lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.01,0:46:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and the joy of realizing now\Nout of compassion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.01,0:46:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is how the body brings about self-healing.\NThe pain then serves a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.14,0:46:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold it now in a different way.\NWe're going to make lemonade out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of going into self-pity about my sickness.\NSee, self-pity is down in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.64,0:46:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of poor me,\Ninstead of being victim, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.70,0:46:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, what is that trying to tell me?\NWhat is it I'm supposed to learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.15,0:46:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get interested in learning\Nabout the nature of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.15,0:46:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We become interested in finding out\Nwhat is underlying this
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.15,0:46:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that we can heal it\Nthrough a greater understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.65,0:46:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first tool that we need then is willingness.\NAn open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.44,0:46:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to say\Nthe mind is doing something that's being asked to be looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.44,0:46:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it can be healed.\NSee, the healing of the body comes about automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.56,0:47:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with the healing of the mind.\NAll the physical illnesses which I eventually let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.56,0:47:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and which healed of their own nature spontaneously\Nall came about as a result of healing the thought forms in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.06,0:47:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the healings came about is\Nthe willingness to let go of self-condemnation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.06,0:47:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the condemnation of others.\NCriticalness, self-pity, resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.19,0:47:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all the things that we see in the box,\Nregret, worry, anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.17,0:47:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,grievances,\Nself-contempt, self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.67,0:47:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the letting go of those things then\Nthat shifted the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.17,0:47:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the energy field is what brought about the healing.\NAnd of course, I worked with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.17,0:47:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept canceling the belief systems,\Nhypoglycemia, gout.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.67,0:47:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As each one would come up, I would cancel it\Nand say, I no longer believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.67,0:47:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer believe in that.\NI'm no longer subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.67,0:47:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the result of a belief system\Nand I have the power of canceling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.20,0:48:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we begin to own that we have the power of denial.\NNot denial in meaning being unconscious of,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.70,0:48:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but the power to refuse.\NI have the power to refuse that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.70,0:48:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have to buy into that.\NNow because these belief systems are so prevalent in our culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.20,0:48:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we naively think, well, they must have a certain reality\Nor everybody wouldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.20,0:48:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reality they have is on the level of a thought form.\NThe fact that there's agreement about a certain thought form
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.70,0:48:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't give it a reality.\NIt only means that there's agreement about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.25,0:48:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can refuse to buy into the collective belief systems\Nabout all these various diseases
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.25,0:48:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I watch it as those programs come in.\NI refuse to believe in cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.25,0:48:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe in AIDS.\NI refuse to believe in all the well-intentioned educational programs
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.25,0:49:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,about all these diseases, hyperglycemia and gout\Nand heart disease and cholesterol.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.25,0:49:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, each one as you buy it, you become subject to it.\NYou're only subject to what you believe in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.75,0:49:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you think eating eggs\Nis going to raise your cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.75,0:49:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and raising your cholesterol is going to give you heart trouble,\Nthen what happens is eating eggs raises your cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.75,0:49:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cholesterol gives you heart trouble\Nbecause of the power of mind. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.75,0:49:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind is so powerful.\NIt creates the thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.75,0:49:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought form then manifests on the physical plane\Nand becomes a physical reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.75,0:49:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you see, self-healing then really depends\Non the reversal of the usual belief system of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.75,0:49:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What you hold in mind manifests on the physical\Nand it's not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.62,0:49:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't eating the cholesterol that gave you the heart problem.\NIt's the belief that eating a lot of cholesterol
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.62,0:50:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,gives you the heart trouble.\NThat's a very critical point to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.12,0:50:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the belief system is sufficient\Nto give you the entire disease picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.62,0:50:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, we mentioned multiple personalities.\NAnd here you see it demonstrated clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.23,0:50:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The one personality that comes into the body,\Nlet's say Dick, and is there for several months,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.76,0:50:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,believes in allergies, believes in cholesterol,\Nbelieves in all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.26,0:50:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he's there, the person has attacks of gout,\Nthe person has migraine headaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.26,0:50:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the person has any of a whole great variety of illnesses.\NHis cholesterol goes up from eating eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.05,0:50:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and he believes in all the fearfulness\Nand all the fearful programs of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.05,0:50:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the other personality is present in the body,\Nnone of that occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.31,0:50:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the belief system,\Nthe mind of the other personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.31,0:50:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,now the body manifests what that mind believes.\NAnd so the person doesn't get hay fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:51:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The person doesn't get asthma.\NHe can eat all the eggs he wants, his cholesterol never goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.50,0:51:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you ask him what he believes about this,\Nhe'll tell you it's all nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.50,0:51:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't believe a word of it.\NIf you don't believe a word of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.16,0:51:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it disappears from your body.\NIt disappears from your body if at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.16,0:51:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you're letting go of the sources of unconscious guilt\Nand you stop reinforcing the illness by labeling it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.16,0:51:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and propagating it\Nand bringing about a fulfillment of your own self-prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.16,0:51:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow the mind to come up with a belief system\Nwithout challenging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.16,0:51:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if the mind unconsciously has been working against us,\Nif we have been unaware of how much power it has,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.16,0:51:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,well, now we can turn around and use that power in our own behalf.\NThat same power which undid us can now work for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.66,0:51:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we consciously utilize the power of mind now.\NSo when the thought comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.16,0:52:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have hypoglycemia, I stop it, I cancel it,\NI say the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.67,0:52:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer subject to that.\NI'm an infinite being. I'm no longer subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.74,0:52:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hypoglycemia is a good example\Nbecause it took me a considerable amount of time to undo that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.74,0:52:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'd given lectures on it for many years.\NIt was operative clinically as an actual physical reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.74,0:52:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I did a lot of work on nutrition,\Nespecially its relationship to the addictions and alcoholism in particular,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.74,0:52:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a very important issue.\NI myself was a firm believer in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.77,0:52:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I came to the understanding\Nand the realization that my firm belief in it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.77,0:52:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was then operating within my body,\Nwhich was expressing my mind's belief in hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.77,0:52:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I had to keep canceling it and keep canceling it,\Nand stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.33,0:53:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, severe hypoglycemia disappeared.\NThe abnormal blood sugars corrected themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.34,0:53:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for many years then,\Nthis was maybe 15 or more years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.84,0:53:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that I finally let go of the belief system in hypoglycemia\Nand recovered from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.34,0:53:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It took some time, though.\NIt took about a year or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.41,0:53:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These various illnesses disappear in different periods of time.\NSome of these illnesses disappeared in a matter of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.41,0:53:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some even disappeared in hours.\NSome took months.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.91,0:53:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This one took longer than almost any of them,\Nother than a block eustachian tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.41,0:53:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That one also took two years.\NI forgot to mention that one in my list of ailments.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.91,0:53:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some 15 years,\NI ate all the sugar and sweets I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.08,0:53:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the reasons which I explained in my weight tape,\NI never gained weight from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.58,0:53:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any hypoglycemic symptoms.\NHypoglycemia just no longer existed in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.11,0:53:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I ate hot fudge sundaes and pecan pie and enjoyed myself.\NAnd then I started giving some lectures locally.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.18,0:54:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked me to give some lectures on hypoglycemia.\NSo I was sort of going back in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.18,0:54:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to sort of a different level of consciousness,\Nto the physical level again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.68,0:54:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I started giving little short talks\Non hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.68,0:54:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would explain how the blood sugar goes up\Nand how the blood sugar goes down and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.68,0:54:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And after giving these talks a few times a month,\Nafter about three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.68,0:54:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I started getting symptoms of hypoglycemia back again.\NI would eat sugar and sweets and I would get the shakes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.68,0:54:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and get feeling anxious and start feeling depressed\Nand emotionally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.68,0:54:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, after all these years,\Nhow could I be getting hypoglycemia back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.68,0:54:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized giving these talks on hypoglycemia\Nhad reactivated the belief system within my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.68,0:54:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I had to stop them.\NI had to cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.21,0:54:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fool myself.\NI can't, on the one hand, not believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.71,0:54:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could split my mind,\Nin which I could, you know, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.71,0:54:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for you folks who still believe in this, this is true,\Nand at the same time split myself and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.21,0:54:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am exempt from that\Nbecause I no longer believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.71,0:55:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I found that that old memory track got reactivated.\NThe belief system in hypoglycemia returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.71,0:55:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I had to re-cancel it.\NAnd so using these talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.06,0:55:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,self-healing systems, this may occur.\NYou may suddenly get the recurrence of something
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.56,0:55:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have to check out what are you doing\Nthat you should be canceling.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.56,0:55:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I began to re-cancel the belief in hypoglycemia\Nand restate the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.06,0:55:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an infinite being.\NI am not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.66,0:55:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And within a month or two,\Nthe symptoms of hypoglycemia disappeared again
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.66,0:55:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and have not returned.\NSo that demonstrates the principle of watchfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.85,0:55:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the mind is that powerful,\Nwe can't let it get away with
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.35,0:55:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that belief system even once.\NEvery time that comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.35,0:55:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am allergic.\NEvery time the thought system comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.35,0:55:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am allergic,\Nit has to be instantly challenged and canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.85,0:55:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One powerful thought, you see,\Nis sufficient to create it on the physical plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.35,0:55:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we can't be sloppy about this work.\NWe have to watch it carefully within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.23,0:56:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There is really no order of difficulty\Nin the curing, in the healing of these various illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.23,0:56:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do we mean by that?\NIt means that what the world considers a severe illness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.23,0:56:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is just as easy to let go of as a minor one.\NIt is just as easy to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.23,0:56:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, to cancel your belief system in coals\Nas it is in cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.33,0:56:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And amongst my friends and acquaintances and co-workers\Nand the people that I have worked with
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.33,0:56:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as Director of the Institute for Spiritual Research in Sedona,\Nthere is a group of people here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.33,0:56:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,who have recovered from every illness known to mankind,\Nall forms of cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.83,0:56:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and multiple sclerosis,\Nand myasthenia gravis,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.83,0:56:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,severe intractable paralyzing illnesses,\Ncomplete and total recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.83,0:56:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Given up as hopeless, given up as almost dead,\Nand yet those people who have become friends of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.83,0:56:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,are extremely alive, extremely well,\Nhave no traces at all of these illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.83,0:57:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't make any difference.\NWhy is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.83,0:57:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the truth is the truth,\Nand that which is false is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.33,0:57:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on the form of the falsehood.\NAll that is false is false,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.33,0:57:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just as all that is true is true.\NIf your mind can create it,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.84,0:57:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,well, then your mind can cancel it.\NSo if you begin to use the power of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.84,0:57:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in your own behalf,\Nhmm, what about the use of medical measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.58,0:57:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the use of traditional medical measures\Nwhile we go about our process of self-healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.08,0:57:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See, our process of self-healing at this point now\Nis being handled on the level of the specific
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.24,0:57:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting go our resistance to experiencing it\Nand canceling it, canceling the thought forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.65,0:57:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The healing is going on in a general,\Nmore powerful way by our willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.65,0:57:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of all criticism and attack\Nand the beginning to love the humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.65,0:58:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in ourself and others,\Nand the reawakening of our awareness of its innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.65,0:58:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the third level,\Nthat is, traditional medical treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.39,0:58:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What part do they play in this kind of self-healing?\NTraditional medical treatments now, surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.42,0:58:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,become very effective.\NWe'll find that as we let go of our guiltiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.55,0:58:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which came about through our lack of compassion\Nfor our own humanness,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.58,0:58:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that medical measures that once were fruitless\Nnow begin to be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.08,0:58:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, all the illnesses I had,\NI was in traditional medical treatment for,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.08,0:58:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for 20 years or more,\Nmigraine headaches and ulcers and diverticulitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.08,0:58:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I was on the diets and I was on the medications\Nand the antispasmodics and the antacids,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.08,0:58:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I did all the traditional medical things,\Nbut they weren't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.34,0:58:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What you could say is they perhaps kept things\Nfrom getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.84,0:59:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I didn't have my stomach taken out, right?\NI didn't have to have the colon removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.34,0:59:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So they were working,\Nbut they were working against all this negative programming
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.34,0:59:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,going on within the mind.\NWhat happens as you let go of all the negative programming
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.50,0:59:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that all these formerly relatively ineffective\Nmedical treatments now become very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.50,0:59:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They become very, very effective.\NSo that the antispasmodic that once barely
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.17,0:59:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,held the symptoms under control\Nnow totally relieves the symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.17,0:59:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A healing comes about.\NThe antispasmodic, the antacids,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.17,0:59:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever diet was considered necessary\Nnow brings about a healing of the ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.17,0:59:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The medications are very powerfully effective.\NThe medications to relieve the allergies
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.17,0:59:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,now work wondrously well.\NAnd we find that the need for the medication
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.67,0:59:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then dwindles off.\NThe need for all these ameliorative measures
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.17,1:00:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,finally disappear.\NAnd so we can resume a normal diet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.76,1:00:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imagine with an elevated cholesterol,\Nhypoglycemia, diverticulitis, an active ulcer,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.76,1:00:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,migraine, and multiple allergies,\Nwhat kind of a diet I must have lived on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.76,1:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I literally remember walking into a restaurant,\Nlooking at the menu,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.26,1:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only thing I could eat on the menu\Nwas the salad and the spinach.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.18,1:00:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there were seeds and things\Nwhich would aggravate the diverticulitis.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.18,1:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was acids which would aggravate the ulcer.\NI couldn't eat tomatoes or anything of that nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.68,1:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, nothing with sugar in it or white bread,\Nso all the pasta, all the bakery,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.68,1:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all the desserts had to go out the window.\NAnd the meat, of course, I had to watch out
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.18,1:00:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the guilt, I mean the guilt, you see,\Nthat was it, the guilt of the gout.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.68,1:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconscious gives you away.\NBecause of the gout, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.68,1:00:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't eat all that meat\Nbecause it would elevate my uric acid level.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.84,1:00:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And so frankly, folks, there was very few\Nthings left on this planet to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.53,1:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But as those things relieved themselves,\Nthen I found that diet was also a belief system.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and that's the downside of holistic health,\Nis the belief system that all these things
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.53,1:01:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are injurious to you.\NThey're injurious to you because
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.03,1:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're holding in mind that they're injurious to you.\NNo such thing exists in the world of the real.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.56,1:01:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I am now on a high-sugar, high-cholesterol,\Nhigh-fat diet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.16,1:01:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My cholesterol, my blood sugar are normal.\NI'm on a high-purine diet,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.16,1:01:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I never get a gout attack, you see.\NThose all turned out to be corollaries to the belief system.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.16,1:01:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a belief system about gout,\Nthen you will have all that goes with it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.66,1:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the various meats that supposedly bring it on,\Nyou know, pickled herring, which I loved, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.45,1:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have it so severe that, you know,\NI just took a little liver pate and put it on a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.45,1:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally, one night full of liver pate\Nwould bring on a gout attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.95,1:02:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can eat a pound of it,\Nand one day I actually did eat a pound of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.45,1:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and liver and kidneys,\Nand I always tell the story of how I one day
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.45,1:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,cooked a frying pan full of liver and kidneys for my kitty,\Nand I thought she loved them,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.20,1:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead she stuck her nose up at them.\NWell, you sort of, as you heal from these illnesses
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.33,1:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,using these techniques we've described today in this talk,\Nyou sort of sometimes just know when you've recovered from something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.83,1:02:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kitty wouldn't eat the kidneys and the liver,\Nand it was a big pan of them, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.83,1:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and it smelled delicious as I was cooking with onions in it\Nand a little bit of bacon, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.83,1:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I even put some catnip in it,\Nand Kitty just wasn't interested.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.83,1:02:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of a sudden I just saw\Nthat my whole dietary limitation
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.83,1:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a crazy belief system I was holding in mind.\NAnd I said, I'm an infinite being.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.86,1:02:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not subject to this.\NI mean, this is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.65,1:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I sat down and, you know,\NI ate a whole pan of kidney and liver,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.65,1:03:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and, needless to say,\NI didn't have a gout attack,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.65,1:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,nor have I ever had one since.\NYou just cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.15,1:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a belief system.\NIt's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.34,1:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sad joke, but it's still a joke.\NIt's a joke that we're only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.84,1:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when we re-own the source of our power,\Nwhen we stop giving it away to the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.34,1:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the cause of God is not in kidneys and liver.\NIt is not in stress.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.84,1:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not in uric acid levels.\NIt has nothing to do with purine metabolism.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.84,1:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with what I hold in mind.\NWhen I re-own,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.84,1:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when I stop denying the power of my own mind,\Nwhen I begin to realize that I am the source,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.34,1:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the source,\Nand by I, what do I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.10,1:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean my consciousness,\Nmy infinite being,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.60,1:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,my infinite being.\NLet's look over at the chart then
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.10,1:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at the physics\Nof how this works.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.60,1:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the intrinsic physics?\NWhat are the energy fuels and what are the levels?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.10,1:04:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, instead of owning myself down here,\Ninstead of putting the power out into the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.11,1:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a lie,\Nwhich is below this energy field here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.24,1:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore the energy field goes that way,\NI begin to re-own the truth about myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.24,1:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My willingness to look into this\Nbrings about the experience of the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.04,1:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by the doingness of this\Nthat you realize the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.54,1:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the scientific purity\Nof what I'm talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.54,1:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about today is pure science,\Nthat you yourself can re-duplicate
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.54,1:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of what I'm saying through your own experimentation,\Nthrough your own individual case.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.46,1:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I re-own myself then as the source,\Nas I move up in my own level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.46,1:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I begin to realize\NI'm not subject to anything except that which I hold in mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.96,1:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has been my belief systems,\Nmy thought forms,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.46,1:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I've brought into,\Nthat have been the cause of what I've been experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.46,1:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The source, the cause of my own experience\Nis what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.46,1:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has no power to create any such thing.\NDoes a piece of kidney have power in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.96,1:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it doesn't.\NDoes my mind have the power?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.96,1:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To create that as a source of disease,\Nyou bet it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.52,1:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we begin to undo the syndrome of the bubble person.\NWhat happens to the bubble person?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.58,1:05:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The bubble person's innocent childlike mind\Nbuys with enthusiasm this whole idea, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.62,1:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of holistic health, nutrition.\NIt begins to read all the literature.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.92,1:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me tell you,\Nif you continue reading that literature long enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.42,1:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you will find that everything in your world\Nand everything in your experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.92,1:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in this universe\Nand everything in your environment will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.92,1:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that is the message you will get.\NMagnesium will kill you. Calcium will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.64,1:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy is given off by the rugs and the paints,\Neverything that's in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.14,1:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if you walk by somebody who's smoking a cigarette,\Nah, I'm going to get cancer of the lung.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.64,1:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All these powerfully negative, you know, thought systems,\Nyou begin to buy into them
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.14,1:06:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretty soon you begin to cancel them one by one.\NI did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.14,1:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to remove one thing after another from my diet.\NI had a friend that says,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.14,1:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,eggs will kill you. Goodbye eggs.\NCholesterol will kill you. Goodbye cholesterol.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.64,1:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Butter will kill you. Dairy products will kill you.\NMeat will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.06,1:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, eat fruit. Okay.\NFruit's full of pesticides. Holy smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.06,1:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was into fruit.\NFruit didn't last long at all
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.56,1:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because the minute you get the pesticide story, goodbye fruit.\NThen I went to vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, vegetables are full of it too.\NThey spray all those fields in California.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.50,1:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You become increasingly paranoid, folks.\NYou don't become increasingly healthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.50,1:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You become increasingly paranoid.\NAnd my brown bag friends are all dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.00,1:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brown bag friends.\NThose are people that used to belong to one of the medical societies
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.00,1:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that really got going on this.\NAnd a brown bag person is one
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.57,1:07:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who has bought so much of this in the world now\Nthat he can only eat one or two grains.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.07,1:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only a few things left on the planet he can eat,\Nwhich he himself, I presume,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.07,1:07:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,has picked somewhere in the fields of Afghanistan or something\Nwhere they don't use pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.57,1:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is carried around in a brown bag.\NSo when he goes to an event
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.57,1:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,where everybody else is eating the banquet, etc.,\Nfull of what he considers to be nothing but poison, you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.57,1:07:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,killing himself with the steak and the pesticides on the peas\Nand the pesticides on the fruit
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.57,1:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the pesticides on the lettuce,\Nwhile in his view they are killing themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.07,1:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he eats out of his brown bag.\NYou see, he sits in the back corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.57,1:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is actually a scene at a big banquet.\NAnd there's a whole table full of brown bag people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.07,1:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, he fasts a lot\Nand he does a lot of running
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.57,1:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and all this kind of stuff.\NAnd, of course, he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.10,1:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he dead?\NA man who did this running every day
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.45,1:08:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and lived this out...\NBecause he became a bubble person
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.95,1:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the paranoid view of the world now\Nbegins to close in on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.95,1:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't breathe the air with trust.\NYou can't believe anything you hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.95,1:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, you see, even enjoy these rugs here\Nbecause they're probably giving off something to which you're allergic.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.95,1:08:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The paints are emanating fumes.\NThe insulation is emanating fumes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.45,1:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fiber particles are choking you up.\NSomebody might have smoked in here
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.95,1:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a smoke particle that's going to give you cancer.\NAnd so your life becomes smaller and smaller and smaller
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.84,1:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because what's happening is you're progressively denying the truth about yourself.\NYou're progressively giving away the power of your being,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.84,1:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of causality to the world,\Nto that which is inanimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.84,1:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening is you're reversing the truth.\NYou're progressively reversing the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.34,1:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you become increasingly vulnerable and victim.\NYou end up with the total paranoia of the bubble person
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.34,1:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who can only live within a protective bubble of purified purification.\NThis is all going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.98,1:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all going on in mind.\NIt's not going on anywhere in reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.48,1:09:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's buying back what is true,\Nbuying back the truth of the power of our own decision
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.98,1:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can cancel that.\NWe are not subject to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.48,1:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an infinite being.\NI am only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.48,1:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the power of canceling.\NI have the power of refusing to buy into that commercial.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.48,1:09:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the power of saying no\Ninstead of buying into the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.48,1:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the power of saying no to family belief systems.\NAllergies may run in my family, and they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.48,1:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother was allergic. My mother was allergic.\NMy sister was allergic.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.48,1:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can say, but that does not apply to me.\NThe truth is, I am only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.48,1:09:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that thought, we heal ourself.\NAmen.
